{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775884141638,"sessionID":"ses_28511ffceffewS2lk4UDYNlI7A","part":{"id":"prt_d7af055780016uMYSp5dhq15Ja","messageID":"msg_d7af0377a001wXqduUkUpQvIIL","sessionID":"ses_28511ffceffewS2lk4UDYNlI7A","type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"toolu_functions.write:18","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/VERIFICATION_REPORT.md","content":"# AgentCube Implementation Verification Report\n\n**AR:** AR-019 — CLI Binary Entry (4 binaries)  \n**Module:** cmd  \n**Language:** Go  \n**Date:** 2026-04-11  \n\n---\n\n## Executive Summary\n\n| Component | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|--------|-------|\n| client-go Library | ❌ **MISSING** | Not implemented - required for CLI binaries |\n| cmd/agentd | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| cmd/router | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| cmd/workload-manager | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| cmd/picod | ❌ **MISSING** | Directory exists, empty |\n| API Types (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1) | ✅ **IMPLEMENTED** | AgentRuntime, CodeInterpreter, Sandbox types defined |\n| Package Implementations | ✅ **IMPLEMENTED** | pkg/agentd, pkg/router, pkg/picod, pkg/workloadmanager |\n\n**Overall Status:** ❌ **NOT COMPLIANT** - Major gaps in required implementation\n\n---\n\n## Detailed Verification\n\n### 1. Client-Go Library (deployment/client-go.md)\n\n**Spec Requirements:**\n- Module path: `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go`\n- API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- Source reference: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n\n**Required Components:**\n\n| Component | Spec Location | Status | Notes |\n|-----------|---------------|--------|-------|\n| **Clientset Interface** | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | ❌ Missing | Should expose `Discovery()`, `RuntimeV1alpha1()` |\n| **Clientset Constructors** | `clientset/versioned/clientset.go` | ❌ Missing | 4 constructors required |\n| **Typed Client Interface** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/runtime_client.go` | ❌ Missing | `RuntimeV1alpha1Interface` |\n| **AgentRuntime Interface** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ❌ Missing | 10 CRUD methods + expansion |\n| **CodeInterpreter Interface** | `typed/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ❌ Missing | Same pattern as AgentRuntime |\n| **Scheme Registration** | `clientset/versioned/scheme/register.go` | ❌ Missing | Scheme, Codecs, ParameterCodec |\n| **Fake Clientset** | `clientset/versioned/fake/` | ❌ Missing | For testing |\n| **SharedInformerFactory** | `informers/externalversions/factory.go` | ❌ Missing | With options, Start/Shutdown/WaitForCacheSync |\n| **Generic Informer** | `informers/externalversions/generic.go` | ❌ Missing | `ForResource()` routing |\n| **AgentRuntime Informer** | `informers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ❌ Missing | |\n| **CodeInterpreter Informer** | `informers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ❌ Missing | |\n| **AgentRuntime Lister** | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime.go` | ❌ Missing | Lister + NamespaceLister |\n| **CodeInterpreter Lister** | `listers/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter.go` | ❌ Missing | Lister + NamespaceLister |\n\n**Verification Command:**\n```bash\n$ ls -la client-go/\nls: cannot access 'client-go/': No such file or directory\n```\n\n**Status:** ❌ **CRITICAL GAP** - The client-go library is completely missing. This is a foundational dependency for the CLI binaries.\n\n---\n\n### 2. CLI Binaries (cmd/)\n\n**Spec Requirements:** 4 binaries as defined in `cmd/design.md`\n\n#### 2.1 cmd/agentd\n\n**Expected:** `cmd/agentd/main.go` (~80 lines)\n- Idle cleanup controller entry point\n- Imports: `pkg/agentd`, `client-go`\n- Configuration: Kubeconfig, SyncPeriod, GracefulTimeout\n- Creates controller-runtime manager\n- Starts AgentRuntime reconciler\n\n**Actual:**\n```bash\n$ ls -la cmd/agentd/\ntotal 8\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 12:14 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n```\n\n**Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n\n---\n\n#### 2.2 cmd/router\n\n**Expected:** `cmd/router/main.go` (~100 lines)\n- Session routing proxy entry point\n- Imports: `pkg/router`, `pkg/store`, `client-go`\n- Configuration: Port, Debug, RedisAddr, WorkloadManagerURL, GracefulTimeout\n- Initializes Gin HTTP server\n- Sets up JWT middleware\n\n**Actual:**\n```bash\n$ ls -la cmd/router/\ntotal 8\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 06:01 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n```\n\n**Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n\n---\n\n#### 2.3 cmd/workload-manager\n\n**Expected:** `cmd/workload-manager/main.go` (~120 lines)\n- Sandbox orchestration entry point\n- Imports: `pkg/workloadmanager`, `client-go`\n- Configuration: Port, Kubeconfig, RedisAddr, DefaultImage, Namespace, GracefulTimeout\n- Creates controller-runtime manager\n- Starts CodeInterpreter controller + HTTP API server\n\n**Actual:**\n```bash\n$ ls -la cmd/workload-manager/\ntotal 8\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 04:21 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n```\n\n**Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n\n---\n\n#### 2.4 cmd/picod\n\n**Expected:** `cmd/picod/main.go` (~90 lines)\n- Sandbox daemon entry point\n- Imports: `pkg/picod`\n- Configuration: Port, Workspace, ReadHeaderTimeout\n- Initializes workspace\n- Starts HTTP server\n\n**Actual:**\n```bash\n$ ls -la cmd/picod/\ntotal 8\ndrwxr-xr-x 2 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 .\ndrwxr-xr-x 6 root root 4096 Apr 11 13:03 ..\n```\n\n**Status:** ❌ **MISSING** - Directory exists but empty\n\n---\n\n### 3. API Types (pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1)\n\n**Verification:** API types are correctly defined\n\n| Type | File | Status | Notes |\n|------|------|--------|-------|\n| `AgentRuntime` | `agentruntime_types.go` | ✅ | Complete with Spec, Status, Conditions |\n| `AgentRuntimeList` | `agentruntime_types.go` | ✅ | Standard Kubernetes list type |\n| `CodeInterpreter` | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | ✅ | Complete with Spec, Status, Conditions |\n| `CodeInterpreterList` | `codeinterpreter_types.go` | ✅ | Standard Kubernetes list type |\n| `Sandbox` | `sandbox_types.go` | ✅ | Present (not in spec but implemented) |\n| `SchemeGroupVersion` | `register.go` | ✅ | `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1` |\n\n**Key Verification Points:**\n- ✅ Group version: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`\n- ✅ Resource plural: `agentruntimes` (from kubebuilder annotation)\n- ✅ Resource plural: `codeinterpreters` (from kubebuilder annotation)\n- ✅ `+genclient` markers present on types\n- ✅ `+k8s:deepcopy-gen` markers present\n\n---\n\n### 4. Package Implementations (pkg/)\n\n| Package | Status | Notes |\n|---------|--------|-------|\n| `pkg/agentd` | ✅ | Reconciler implementation present |\n| `pkg/router` | ✅ | JWT, handlers, middleware present |\n| `pkg/picod` | ✅ | Sandbox daemon implementation present |\n| `pkg/workloadmanager` | ✅ | Controller, service, types present |\n| `pkg/store` | ✅ | Redis/Valkey store implementation |\n| `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` | ✅ | API types with deepcopy generation |\n\n---\n\n## Dependency Analysis\n\n### Go Module (go.mod)\n\n**Status:** ✅ Present and correctly configured\n\n**Key Dependencies:**\n- `k8s.io/client-go v0.32.0` ✅\n- `k8s.io/api v0.32.0` ✅\n- `k8s.io/apimachinery v0.32.0` ✅\n- `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime v0.19.0` ✅\n\n**Missing Dependency:**\n- `github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/client-go` ❌ - This should be a local submodule or internal package\n\n---\n\n## Test Status\n\n```\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/agentd    (cached)\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1       (cached)\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/picod/jwt (cached)\nok      github.com/volcano-sh/agentcube/pkg/store     (cached)\n```\n\n**Note:** Tests pass for existing packages, but there are many packages with `[no test files]`. This is acceptable for the `cmd/` binaries as they are thin wrappers, but the client-go library would need comprehensive tests.\n\n---\n\n## Build Verification\n\n```bash\n$ go build ./...\n# Success - no errors\n```\n\n**Note:** Build succeeds because the missing `client-go` and `cmd/*` are not imported by existing code. The design documents reference them, but the actual import statements don't exist.\n\n---\n\n## Compliance Matrix\n\n| Requirement | Spec Location | Implementation | Status |\n|-------------|---------------|----------------|--------|\n| Clientset Interface | client-go.md:19-22 | Missing | ❌ |\n| Clientset Constructors | client-go.md:29-34 | Missing | ❌ |\n| RuntimeV1alpha1Interface | client-go.md:44-49 | Missing | ❌ |\n| AgentRuntimeInterface | client-go.md:61-72 | Missing | ❌ |\n| CodeInterpreterInterface | client-go.md:79 | Missing | ❌ |\n| Scheme Registration | client-go.md:96-101 | Missing | ❌ |\n| SharedInformerFactory | client-go.md:109-127 | Missing | ❌ |\n| AgentRuntime Informer | client-go.md:152-158 | Missing | ❌ |\n| AgentRuntime Lister | client-go.md:184-199 | Missing | ❌ |\n| Fake Clientset | client-go.md:210-217 | Missing | ❌ |\n| cmd/agentd/main.go | cmd/design.md:125 | Missing | ❌ |\n| cmd/router/main.go | cmd/design.md:127 | Missing | ❌ |\n| cmd/workload-manager/main.go | cmd/design.md:129 | Missing | ❌ |\n| cmd/picod/main.go | cmd/design.md:131 | Missing | ❌ |\n| API Types | pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1 | Present | ✅ |\n\n---\n\n## Blockers for Completion\n\n1. **client-go Library Generation** (P0 - Critical)\n   - Must generate typed clients for AgentRuntime and CodeInterpreter\n   - Requires code-generator or manual implementation\n   - Blocks all Kubernetes-dependent binaries\n\n2. **Binary Implementation** (P0 - Critical)\n   - Each binary needs main.go with:\n     - Flag parsing\n     - Configuration validation\n     - Dependency initialization\n     - Graceful shutdown handling\n     - Service startup\n\n---\n\n## Recommendations\n\n### Option 1: Generate client-go using code-generator\n1. Add `k8s.io/code-generator` to tools\n2. Create `hack/update-codegen.sh` script\n3. Run generation to create client-go/ directory\n4. Implement cmd/* binaries using generated client\n\n### Option 2: Manual client-go implementation\n1. Implement typed clients manually\n2. Create clientset, informers, listers as per spec\n3. More work but complete control over implementation\n\n### Option 3: Use controller-runtime client directly\n1. Skip client-go generation\n2. Use `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/client` in binaries\n3. Simpler but deviates from spec\n\n---\n\n## Conclusion\n\nThe **AR-019 CLI Binary Entry** implementation is **NOT COMPLIANT** with the specification. While the underlying package implementations (`pkg/*`) and API types are complete, the critical deliverables are missing:\n\n1. The `client-go` library is entirely absent - this is a foundational requirement\n2. All 4 CLI binary entry points (`cmd/*`) are empty directories\n\nTo achieve compliance, the client-go library must be generated (or manually implemented) following the exact structure specified in `deployment/client-go.md`, and then the 4 CLI binaries must be implemented as thin wrappers around the existing `pkg/*` implementations.\n\n**Estimated Remaining Work:**\n- client-go generation: ~4-6 hours\n- cmd/* binary implementation: ~2-3 hours each (8-12 hours total)\n- Testing and integration: ~4 hours\n- **Total: ~16-22 hours**\n\n---\n\n*Report generated by quality-gate verification process*\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/register.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/agentruntime_types.go":[],"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-kimi-k2.5_20260410T163138Z/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/codeinterpreter_types.go":[]},